import React,{useState,useEffect} from 'react' import axios from 'axios' import Header from './Header' import {Container,Card} from 'react-bootstrap' function UserViewApp() { const [app,setApp] = useState({}) const [confirmation,setConfirmation] = useState('') const id = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem('appId')) const viewApplication = async()=>{ const appDetails = await axios.get(`http://localhost:4000/admin/viewapplication/${id[0]}`) setApp(appDetails.data.data) } useEffect(()=>{ viewApplication() },[]) return ( <>

) } export default UserViewApp
